Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.16,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰人能得見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:03.18,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}誰人能知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:07.20,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}似朝霧沉沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:11.77,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}將熹光籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.92,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}奇蹟之事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.61,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}將由誰創造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.10,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}無人能定調
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:25.45,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}在磚瓦路上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:29.25,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}於思考之前出招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.49,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.49,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}渾身上下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:39.16,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}都在奮力呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.60,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}因僅憑一顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.75,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}拚盡全力生息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:47.29,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}苦痛纏身在即
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:50.74,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要踏出一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.84,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}世界就會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.28,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}想像外的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:57.54,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}也能現於眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.81,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只需相信便好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:06.59,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}鐵杵尚能磨成針
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.81,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}你我一定也可以
